---
import DemoLayout from '../../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';
---

<DemoLayout
  title="DNSSEC"
  description="DNSSEC adds an extra layer of authentication layer to DNS, making sure that visitors go to your domain instead of a spoofed domain."
  category="Application Security"
  labels={["DNS", "DNSSEC"]}
  lastUpdated="April 2025"
>

  <!-- Overview Card -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
    <h2 id="overview-heading">Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Cloudflare offers comprehensive DNS solutions as an Authoritative DNS Provider including{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/zone-setups/full-setup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Full DNS Setup</a>,{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/zone-setups/partial-setup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">CNAME Setup</a>,
      and{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/zone-setups/zone-transfers/cloudflare-as-secondary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Secondary DNS</a>.
      The globally distributed Anycast network consistently ranks among the{' '}
      <a href="https://www.dnsperf.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">fastest DNS providers worldwide</a>.
      Additionally,{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/dnssec/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">DNSSEC</a>
      {' '}adds an extra layer of authentication to DNS, preventing domain spoofing, while{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/additional-options/analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">DNS Analytics</a>
      {' '}provides detailed insights into your DNS traffic.
    </p>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">NSEC3</h3>
    <p>
      Cloudflare's implementation of negative answers with NSEC is protected against zone walking. This implementation
      removes the need for{' '}
      <a href="https://dnsinstitute.com/documentation/dnssec-guide/ch06s02.html" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">NSEC3</a>
      {' '}and has been{' '}
      <a href="https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-dnsop-compact-denial-of-existence/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">proposed as an IETF standard</a>.
      If you must use NSEC3 for compliance reasons, you can{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/api/resources/dns/subresources/dnssec/methods/edit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">enable it via API</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="btn-row">
      <a
        href="https://dnsviz.net/d/automatic-demo.com/analyze/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer external"
        class="btn btn-secondary"
      >
        Visit Demo
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DNSSEC Settings Screenshot -->
  <section aria-labelledby="settings-heading">
    <h2 id="settings-heading">DNSSEC Settings</h2>
    <div class="img-container">
      <img
        src="/demos/performance/img/cf-zone-dnssec.png"
        alt="Zone DNSSEC Dashboard Settings"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DNS Analytics Video -->
  <section aria-labelledby="analytics-heading">
    <h2 id="analytics-heading">DNS Analytics</h2>
    <div class="video-container">
      <iframe
        src="https://customer-px4ru5rucxtgoo68.cloudflarestream.com/f92a7e38dfe749b6c2a532e7dcd0a831/iframe?muted=true&preload=true&loop=true&autoplay=true&poster=https%3A%2F%2Fcustomer-px4ru5rucxtgoo68.cloudflarestream.com%2Ff92a7e38dfe749b6c2a532e7dcd0a831%2Fthumbnails%2Fthumbnail.jpg%3Ftime%3D%26height%3D600&title=Zone+DNS+Analytics"
        loading="lazy"
        allow="accelerometer; gyroscope; autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;"
        allowfullscreen
        title="Zone DNS Analytics"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DoH Examples -->
  <section aria-labelledby="doh-heading">
    <h2 id="doh-heading">Public DNS Resolver - Query Examples</h2>
    <p>
      Cloudflare also offers a public DNS resolver{' '}
      <a href="https://one.one.one.one/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">1.1.1.1</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="code-block mt-1">
      <h3 class="code-label">
        DNS Query via{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/1.1.1.1/encryption/dns-over-https/make-api-requests/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
          DNS over HTTPS (DoH)
        </a>
        {' '}- JSON Response
      </h3>
      <pre><code>curl -H 'accept: application/dns-json' 'https://cloudflare-dns.com/dns-query?name=automatic-demo.com&type=A' | jq .</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="code-block mt-1">
      <h3 class="code-label">DNS Query via DoH - Headers Response</h3>
      <pre><code>curl -I --doh-url https://cloudflare-dns.com/dns-query https://automatic-demo.com</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

</DemoLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Section spacing ===== */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section > h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 1.45rem);
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== Card ===== */
  .card {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  }

  .card p, section > p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Subsection heading ===== */
  .subsection-heading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ===== Utility ===== */
  .mt-1 { margin-top: 1rem; }

  /* ===== Button Row ===== */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: var(--secondary);
    color: white;
  }

  /* ===== Image Container ===== */
  .img-container {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .img-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ===== Video Container ===== */
  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 56.67%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    border: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* ===== Code Block ===== */
  .code-block {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .code-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ===== Mobile ===== */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .btn-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .btn { text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
